==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*εἰρήνη / eirēnē / i-rah'-nay

===Etymology===
*Probably from a primary verb εἴρω eirō (to join); peace (literally or figuratively); by implication prosperity:

===Noun===
'''εἰρήνη'''

# one, [[peace]], [[quietness]], [[rest]], + set at one again.

